{"tid":2323693,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利男子同老婆鬧交 谷鳩氣之下行咗400公里！","createTime":"2020-12-13T11:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T17:06:57.000Z","uid":197125,"like":76,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7c209878ba61d36250663810360355fa1e3beef6","tid":2323693,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T11:11:53.000Z","msg":"#國際大小事：真係咁嬲？😅😅😅<br />\n<br />\n最近意大利一名男士因違反封城令，被當地警察攔下。一查之下發現該名男士居住於超過400公里外的城鎮！🧐<br />\n<br />\n男子原居於意瑞邊境的城鎮Como，但警方卻於凌晨2點在400公里外的小鎮Fano攔下佢。男子解釋話一星期前同老婆嗌交，佢為咗令自己冷靜落嚟行足一星期，行到嚟呢度，計落每日行超過64km！🤯<br />\n<br />\n警方立即同佢的妻子聯絡，確認事件。男子\b被發現時清醒，佢表示有點累，亦有點凍，但唔知自己行咗幾遠。佢表示一星期以來都係靠陌生人提供食物😳<br />\n<br />\n男子最後被安排於酒店逗留，佢老婆嚟到接佢後，除咗要俾酒店錢外，仲要俾&euro;400罰款😶 希望佢哋唔好再嗌交啦🤭<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/italy-lockdown-walk-como-fano-b1766397.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fitaly-lockdown-walk-como-fano-b1766397.html&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mYRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=1f85caa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/italy-lockdown-walk-como-fano-b1766397.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom fb: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/192678424122112/posts/3742131295843456/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F192678424122112%2Fposts%2F3742131295843456%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mYRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=6bcb34e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/192678424122112/posts/3742131295843456/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n真行路撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人學下嘢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0501197f36d2a5dd8e507c72c190a531efa98ae","tid":2323693,"uid":383593,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"嬲到瘋狂行路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31277b